variales banate hain data ko store krne k lye variable hi js ka structure khelo kyu k is k ander hi hum data ko store kr k phir operations kr te hain

variables total 3 tarekon k hote hain 
1, var
2, let
3, const 


var kyu k kafi purana hogya or ye abb safe bhi nhi hai tw iss se ko use nhi kr ta isi lye hum bhi isse use nhi kr te 

let ek normal varibale hai jo k se hota hai noramlly

const ek thora unique hai kyu k ager apne is k ander koi datastore kr dya os k baad app isse change nhi kr sakte al batttta let me change ho sakta hai 




kisi bho variable ko string me krne k lye "" is k ander likh te hain mthlb wo string hai abb ye number alphabet kuch bhi ho sakta hai and string ki indexxing 0 se churu hoti hai

strings k kafi sare methods bhi hote hain

string ki lenght malum krne k lye .lenght use krte hain

ager string bare alphabet me chaiye tw toUpperCase()
ager string chote alphabet me chaiye tw toLowerCase()

slice() issse value cut hoti hai

or ager 2 strings merge krni hai tw concat() ka istamal karo





array use hota hai multiple values ko store krne k lye and is ki bhi indexxing 0 se hi churu hoti hai
array k bhi kafi are methods hote hain:

toString() is se data string me convert ho jata hai
pop()      is se array ka last data jo bhi hoga wo cut hojai ga
push()     is se array k akhir me data dal sakte hain   
shift()    is se phele wala data nikalta hai
unshift()  is se churu me data add kr sakte hain
splice()   is se data cut hota hai
map()      ye sare elements ko modify kr ta hai ek new array k ander bhot kam ki cheezz hai
filter()   ager koi condition lagani hai or  chate ho k ager ye ho tw ye cheezien chalein tw is ka use karo








comman cheezien js ki:

alert()
alert se ek popup ata hai website per bhot sari websites me ata hai

confirm()
cancel krta hai popup true/false k sath


parseInt()
string ko intergert me badal ta hai



isNaN()
dekh ta hai value number tou nhi



toString()
number ko string me badal ta hai




console.log()
console me print hoker ata hai is se


Math.random()
0 - 1 k beech me koi bhi random number generate kr ta hai



Math.floor()
Rounds a number down to the nearest interger



Math.cell()
Rounds a number up to the nearest interger



Math.max()
Returns the largest to the given number




Math.min()
Return the largest to the given numbers




Date()
Return the smallest to the given numbers



Date()
Return the current date and time





