if( ider contion aiigi ){

} else{
    
}





function ek block of code hota hai jo ek specific kaam karta hai, aur use baar-baar call karke reuse kiya ja sakta hai

arrow function bhi hota hai





classlist
class add krne k lye classlist.add and remove krne ke lye class.remove use krte hain

innerHTML, textContent
kisi bhi element me html likh ne k lye


settimeout 
ye ye hota hai k time deker app kisi bhi cheez ko kitni bhi der se lasakte ho


setInterval() 
function kisi function ko repeat karne ke liye use hota hai

try catch
ye ye krna hai ager app is k ander apna code likhinge or ager koi error hoga tw ye app ko bata dega

locaclstorage
browser me ek storage hoti hai localstorage k name se is k ander user ka data hum rakh sakte hain temprary


onclick()
is hum html me likh te hain kisi bhi cheez per or phir is k oper jo js likhoge wo chalegi

loops
ek for loop hota hai, ek for each hota hai and or bhi hote hain per commanly ye hi use ote hain
loops ek cheez ko bar bar repititive kr ne k lye use krte hain


async await
js work krti hai ager app ne koi function banaya or app chate ho k ye visible hoe thori der k baad tw os k baadd jitni bhi js hogi wo rukh jaigi bolegi phele ye chale phir hi me ageey barunga per async await os se bolta hai k js ko na roko





dom se hum id ya class jo bhi hai get kr te hain get kr ne k total 5 tareeke hain 
id,classname, queryselector,querllyselectorall, bytagname

id sirf ek element k lye get hoti hai 
tag se jo bhi tag ho ga on sare per lag jaiga 
all sse sare elements per lagega
query selector se sirf ek per lagega

addEventListener()
Adds an event handller to an element
removeEventListener()
Removes and event from an element







